{"tid":823204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人面對風暴","createTime":"2018-09-16T16:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T17:46:53.000Z","uid":201299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"708d1e5fe890d861f1d587dcc2a4cd589d995ae5","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:48:52.000Z","msg":"十二月，熱帶風暴布拉曼登陸越南，損失千萬；香港人在工作中。<br />\n二月，熱帶風暴三巴擊中菲律賓，共十四人死亡；香港人仍在OT中。<br />\n六月頭，熱帶風暴艾維尼吹襲中國南部，釀成五億損失；香港人放工迫地鐵回家。<br />\n六月尾，颱風巴比侖吹過日、韓，當地緊固建築亦抵受不住強風；香港人在食飯盒。<br />\n七月頭，颱風瑪莉亞吹襲台灣，當局宣佈停工停課；香港人打開電視機。<br />\n八月頭，颱風貝碧佳盤旋於華南沿岸上空；香港終於懸掛三號強風信號。<br />\n八月尾，颱風燕子吹襲日本，當地橋梁等基建倒塌；香港人對著電腦工作。<br />\n九月，颱風山竹橫掃廣東，深圳、澳門停工停課，港珠澳人工島陸沉；香港人仍謹記<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝準時返工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac677e944ab2e15c2cdc15b9cea88ac0d0094d","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbcb917b4af14544115fff0a0e3324ae4a6b9c1","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b64b614ab24d0f3f6d4490199b4e5cf138d5b2","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"波台狗：濕濕碎"},{"pid":"a187117dba58320fc77792c579f5a4a668089e69","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"俾啲反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2be9b5a8bea9e7cd6de30b3737b399b1baf06ba","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f32300dcc800b9d11c32e3b5b4bee2feefc9764","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca2c966d695d697fb0040cabd7a2d23e850e55","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"天文台我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f93b1f9c9264f17cdeb4693b8bfc8dfdf59490c","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74836605beb9869a276cac5ffc3b87697702a29d","tid":823204,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}